---
// src/components/HowItWorks.astro
---
<section id="como-funciona" class="how-it-works">
  <div class="hiw-container">
    <div class="hiw-badge">Cómo Funciona</div>
    <h2>Automatizá tu negocio en <span>3 simples pasos</span></h2>
    <p class="hiw-subtitle">
      Sin código, sin complicaciones. Conectá tus canales, configurá tu chatbot y empezá a cerrar ventas en minutos.
    </p>

    <div class="steps-timeline">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">01</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="32" height="32">
            <path d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Conectá tus canales</h3>
        <p>Integrá WhatsApp, Instagram y Facebook Messenger en una sola bandeja de entrada unificada.</p>
        <div class="step-tags">
          <span class="tag">WhatsApp</span>
          <span class="tag">Instagram</span>
          <span class="tag">Messenger</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Connector -->
      <div class="step-connector">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 60 24" width="60" height="24">
          <path d="M0 12h50m-8-8l8 8-8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">02</div>
        <div class="step-icon step-icon-purple">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="32" height="32">
            <path d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Configurá tu chatbot IA</h3>
        <p>Personalizá las respuestas automáticas, flujos de venta y clasificación de prospectos con nuestra IA.</p>
        <div class="step-tags">
          <span class="tag purple">IA Avanzada</span>
          <span class="tag purple">No-Code</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Connector -->
      <div class="step-connector">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 60 24" width="60" height="24">
          <path d="M0 12h50m-8-8l8 8-8 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">03</div>
        <div class="step-icon step-icon-green">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="32" height="32">
            <path d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Vendé mientras dormís</h3>
        <p>Tu chatbot responde, califica y agenda clientes 24/7. Vos solo cerrás las ventas.</p>
        <div class="step-tags">
          <span class="tag green">24/7</span>
          <span class="tag green">Automático</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom visual: Live preview mockup -->
    <div class="hiw-demo-bar">
      <div class="demo-dot green-pulse"></div>
      <span>SmartInbox procesó <strong>1,247 mensajes</strong> en las últimas 24 horas</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    padding: 7rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8f9ff 0%, #ffffff 50%, #f0fdf4 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .how-it-works::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 800px;
    height: 800px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.03) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hiw-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    width: 90%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hiw-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.08), rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.15));
    color: var(--color-primary-green);
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.12);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  h2 span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-green), #22c55e);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hiw-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-medium);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }

  .steps-timeline {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .step-connector {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem;
    max-width: 300px;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: left;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .step-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary-blue), var(--color-primary-green));
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.35s;
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 48px rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.12);
  }

  .step-card:hover::after {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .step-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1rem;
    right: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.06);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.08), rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.15));
    color: var(--color-primary-blue);
    transition: transform 0.35s;
  }

  .step-icon-purple {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08), rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15));
    color: #8b5cf6;
  }

  .step-icon-green {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.08), rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.15));
    color: var(--color-primary-green);
  }

  .step-card:hover .step-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-3deg);
  }

  .step-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .step-card p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-medium);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .step-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tag {
    background: rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.06);
    color: var(--color-primary-blue);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .tag.purple {
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.06);
    color: #8b5cf6;
  }

  .tag.green {
    background: rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.06);
    color: var(--color-primary-green);
  }

  /* Demo bar */
  .hiw-demo-bar {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-medium);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }

  .hiw-demo-bar strong {
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
  }

  .demo-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .green-pulse {
    background: var(--color-primary-green);
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.4); }
    50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(21, 198, 59, 0); }
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .steps-timeline {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .step-connector {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
    .step-card {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .how-it-works {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    .hiw-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .step-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    .hiw-demo-bar {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
